(133, 4, '2013-09-15 03:58:39', '2013-09-15 03:58:39', 'Trans people often have difficulties obtaining clothing when they transition to their new gender. Also many of us simply throw away or donate our old clothes, then we must purchase new clothes we sometimes cannot afford.\r\n\r\nTransH4ack ClothesR4ck is a new app to enable MtF and FtM, Gender Variant and GenderQueer folks to exchange clothes and recieve donations of clothes and clothing gift cards.\r\n\r\nAll people will earn points by answering inclusive trans historical and trans positive questions.\r\n\r\nThis app enables MTF and FTM folks as well as genderqueer, gendervariant, genderqueer and genderfabulous folks to build community, share clothes, and exchange community support from each other. In order to acces the system alll people must be able to answer trans positive questions therfore the app will also build knowledge with non trans allies.', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '40-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-15 03:58:39', '2013-09-15 03:58:39', '', 40, 'http://ec2-54-215-179-94.us-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com
/transhackclothesrack/2013/09/40-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(134, 4, '2013-09-15 04:33:23', '2013-09-15 04:33:23', 'As trans* people, we often have difficulties obtaining clothing while in transition. Many of us simply throw away or donate old clothes, then acquire new clothes we sometimes cannot afford.\n\n<span style="color:#e10707;font-weight:bold">TransH4ack ClothesR4ck</span> is a new site to facilitate trans*, gender variant and genderqueer people exchanging clothes. Participants and allies also encouraged to donate to help support shipping costs for those who otherwise couldn''t afford to participate.\n\nTrans-specific and inclusive tech like TransH4CK ClothesR4CK helps us share in something more important than clothes -- it hl to share in our own community.', 'How it Works', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '40-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-15 04:33:23', '2013-09-15 04:33:23', '', 40, 'http://ec2-54-215-179-94.us-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com
